column2: Amber Heard was proven guilty in the Depp trial. It is not a good look for a huge franchise to be attached to her. She is overshadowing the franchise; in my opinion. All promos you will hear about her losing her defamation case to Johnny Depp. The publicity for Aquaman 2, etc. will be a reminder of the case. I am sure most of us want to enjoy Aquaman [Jason Mamoa] and have her face on the screen as a constant reminder of that trial.

column34: Amber Heard is abusive. She is not a fit role model to be seen in movies. She abused Johnny Depp and has no remorse or regret. There are plenty of video and audio evidence to attest to this. She also cheated on him twice. If you are going to remove Johnny from Grindelwald, then you should remove her as well. There are plenty of better, more talented and non-abusive actresses that you could choose from. But either way, if you refuse to recast her we will boycott. Choose wisely Warner Bros.

There are plenty of video and audio evidence to attest to this. She also cheated on him twice. If you are going to remove Johnny from Grindelwald, then you should remove her as well. There are plenty of better, more talented and non-abusive actresses that you could choose from. But either way, if you refuse to recast her we will boycott. Choose wisely Warner Bros.
